{"word":"H7853 - שָׂטַן - sâṭan - saw-tan' - Adversary","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׂטַן</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>sâṭan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>saw-tan'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Adversary"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - விரோதஞ்செய், விரோதி, விரோதிக்கிறவர்கள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(Qal) to be or act as an adversary, to resist, to oppose"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>attack</i>, (figuratively) <i>accuse: - </i>(be an) adversary, resist."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7853 - שָׂטַן - sâṭan - saw-tan'/7853\">H7853</a>, <a href=\"#/H7854 - שָׂטָן - sâṭân - saw-tawn'/7854\">H7854</a>, <a href=\"#/H7855 - שִׂטְנָה - siṭnâh - sit-naw'/7855\">H7855</a>, <a href=\"#/H7856 - שִׂטְנָה - Siṭnâh - sit-naw'/7856\">H7856</a>"}]}